  "2209900": {
    "name": "Moonlight Peaks",
    "steam_appid": 2209900,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/56bf33ec3948493007f44dc13c5a9a18.avif?t=1766966306\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Moonlight Peaks》的魔法小镇中体验吸血鬼的生活！在这款温暖人心的生活模拟游戏中，你需要向持怀疑态度的父亲德古拉伯爵证明，带着善意度过一生是完全可以实现的——即使对于不死一族来说也是如此。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与当地的狼人、女巫和美人鱼交朋友，在超自然的约会场景中寻找永恒的爱情。拥抱不朽并解锁远古力量、酿制药水和施放咒语。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开居住在《Moonlight Peaks》的七大家族的种种谜团，并走出你父亲的阴影。你作为一名Dracula的遗产要由你亲手打造！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>寻找你的完美伴侣</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Moonlight Peaks》，相亲池里装满了药水。从狼人到人类，在无所不包的芸芸众生中找到你的天生伴侣。你们甚至可能会决定长相厮守直到永远…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/ded82ae14b24966ccdb4a64d80b11fdd.avif?t=1766966306\" width=604 height=1402 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>种植并收获魔法农作物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >悉心照料一个温馨的农场，里面长满了魔法农作物和会发光的鲜花！作为一个吸血鬼，你以附魔食物维生，因此照料好你的花园不只是一个爱好——它是你日常生活的一部分。对你的工具施魔，并观看你的农作物自行茁壮成长……还有别忘了给予你的Draculambs一只应得的宠物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/d0ba44ee1d3b2697941bd32caa9cccc0.poster.avif?t=1766966306\" width=604 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/d0ba44ee1d3b2697941bd32caa9cccc0.webm?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/d0ba44ee1d3b2697941bd32caa9cccc0.mp4?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>有型有款地拥抱吸血人生</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从种类繁多的自定义选项中进行选择，创建一个能真正代表你的角色。随着你在游戏中不断推进，你还将解锁强大的吸血鬼能力，让你显现出你那些不朽祖先们所独有的特征。从经过强化的感官到全情投入的变身，这些能力会让在《Moonlight Peaks》停留的每一天都成为一趟难以忘怀的冒险之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/beb52ab653367e15f210e5f0b2a8fd45.poster.avif?t=1766966306\" width=604 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/beb52ab653367e15f210e5f0b2a8fd45.webm?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/beb52ab653367e15f210e5f0b2a8fd45.mp4?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造你的梦幻吸血鬼圣所</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建属于自己的吸血鬼天堂，一个体现你哥特式品味的圣所。选择完美的棺材，制作怪诞的装饰，为你的家营造出恐怖的氛围。农场地块可以扩张，房屋也可以升级，为你提供无限的可能性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/ba7cfd06f62f7d8b7898bbf0dc5b7e68.poster.avif?t=1766966306\" width=604 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/ba7cfd06f62f7d8b7898bbf0dc5b7e68.webm?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/ba7cfd06f62f7d8b7898bbf0dc5b7e68.mp4?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>掌握巫术的艺术</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Moonlight Peaks》，药水制作和咒语施放的艺术是日常生活不可或缺的组成部分。在学习咒语时师从本地女巫，用稀有的原料做实验，并酿制强大的药水以助力你的冒险之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/da20e92af48c864e5fdae0b099bd5a44.poster.avif?t=1766966306\" width=604 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/da20e92af48c864e5fdae0b099bd5a44.webm?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/da20e92af48c864e5fdae0b099bd5a44.mp4?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索一个超自然世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集魔法原料，准备附魔餐食，并参与季节性活动。使用你的变身能力来发现潜藏着远古秘密的隐秘角落。从充满活力的村庄街道，到迷雾笼罩的森林深处，探索一个充满了奇迹与阴谋的领域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/1f2e37530efb8a0ef069995d028b5ec3.poster.avif?t=1766966306\" width=604 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/1f2e37530efb8a0ef069995d028b5ec3.webm?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/1f2e37530efb8a0ef069995d028b5ec3.mp4?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>月光照耀的迷你游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >停下冒险的脚步稍作休息，体会各种魅力十足的活动，例如制作陶艺、插花以及为你的动物们演奏小提琴。无论是熟练掌握Nokturna——本地卡牌游戏——还是参与《Moonlight Peaks》的年度厨艺大赛，总有新鲜内容可供探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/d1c199abec899c28dbaaf7a6ce84dd68.poster.avif?t=1766966306\" width=604 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/d1c199abec899c28dbaaf7a6ce84dd68.webm?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209900/extras/d1c199abec899c28dbaaf7a6ce84dd68.mp4?t=1766966306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
